  17,17,Multus generation habet nos annihilated Noah. Tuus Dominus est efficient in dealing cum sins His servus; He est fully Cognizant Seer
  17,18,Anyone chooses hoc fleeting vita his priority nos rush eum quod nos decide dedit eum tunc nos commit eum Gehenna he suffers forever despised defeated
